OL,3,CArena attack survivor 'shouldn't need
OL,4,Ccourt to prove not faked'
OL,6,FA survivor of the Manchester Arena
OL,7,Fbombing says he should never have had
OL,8,Fto go to court to hear allegations
OL,9,Fthat the attack was 'fake'.
OL,11,FIt comes after the conclusion of the
OL,12,Fthe trial at the High Court in London
OL,13,Fof a former television producer who
OL,14,Fclaims that the bombing was a 'lie'.
OL,16,FMartin Hibbert and his daughter Eve
OL,17,Fsuffered serious injuries in the
OL,18,Fattack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
