OL,3,CArena attack survivor 'shouldn't need
OL,4,Ccourt to prove not faked'
OL,6,FThey've brought legal action for
OL,7,Fharassment and data protection against
OL,8,FRichard Hall over several videos and a
OL,9,Fbook where he claims the bombing was a
OL,10,F"hoax", as well as "secretly filming"
OL,11,FMiss Hibbert and her mother at their
OL,12,Fhouse.
OL,14,FIn a statement following today's
OL,15,Fhearing Mr. Hibbert said: "I would
OL,16,Flike to thank my team at Hudgell
OL,17,FSolicitors and my barrister Jonathan
OL,18,FPrice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
