OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1722004378
OL,3,CArena attack survivor 'shouldn't need
OL,4,Ccourt to prove not faked'
OL,6,F"They and I believe this has been an
OL,7,Fextremely important case to bring to
OL,8,Fcourt.
OL,10,F"We live in a society where free
OL,11,Fspeech and the right to express a
OL,12,Fgenuinely held opinion must be
OL,13,Fprotected, but when those beliefs and
OL,14,Factions are inaccurate, offensive and
OL,15,Fdamaging, and cause harm to those who
OL,16,Fhave already suffered so badly, people
OL,17,Fmust be challenged.
OL,19,F"Actions that in this case have led to
OL,20,Ffurther anxiety and distress."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
