OL,3,CArena attack survivor 'shouldn't need
OL,4,Ccourt to prove not faked'
OL,6,FMartin continued: "We shouldn't have
OL,7,Fto face such allegations that the
OL,8,FManchester Arena attack never
OL,9,Fhappened, and that our injuries were
OL,10,Fnot as a result of the bombing ` we
OL,11,Fcertainly shouldn't have needed to be
OL,12,Fhere in court to make a stand and to
OL,13,Fprotect others from this kind of
OL,14,Fbehaviour.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
