OL,3,CArena attack survivor 'shouldn't need
OL,4,Ccourt to prove not faked'
OL,6,F"For many families affected by the
OL,7,Fbombing it is struggle every day, even
OL,8,Fnow more than seven years on, to
OL,9,Fcomprehend what happened, and the
OL,10,Fimpact it has had on their lives. They
OL,11,Fshould never have to face such hurtful
OL,12,Fclaims and I hope this case sends out
OL,13,Fa clear message that it will not be
OL,14,Ftolerated."
OL,16,FMartin and his daughter Eve were at
OL,17,Fthe Ariana Grande concert in May 2017.
OL,19,FHe sustained a spinal cord injury -
OL,20,Fleaving him paralysed - and Eve was
OL,21,Fleft with a catastrophic brain injury.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
