OL,3,CArena attack survivor 'shouldn't need
OL,4,Ccourt to prove not faked'
OL,6,FThe court heard Mr Hall claim that
OL,7,F"Millions of people have bought a
OL,8,Flie," that "there was no bomb" and
OL,9,Fthat the public inquiry into the
OL,10,Fattack "ignored" evidence.
OL,12,FHe also told the court that he
OL,13,Fbelieved that no one was "genuinely
OL,14,Finjured" in the attack, with evidence
OL,15,Fshowing the incident was "faked".
OL,17,FBut Mr Hall has claimed his actions -
OL,18,Fincluding an incident of filming Miss
OL,19,FHibbert outside her home - were in the
OL,20,Fpublic interest as a journalist.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
