OL,3,CArena attack survivor 'shouldn't need
OL,4,Ccourt to prove not faked'
OL,6,FHe told the London court: "The primary
OL,7,Fevidence shows there was no bomb in
OL,8,Fthat room that exploded."
OL,10,FAfter a three-and-a-half-day trial,
OL,11,FMrs Justice Steyn said on Thursday
OL,12,Fthat she would give her decision on
OL,13,Fthe claim in writing at a later date.
OL,15,FSpeaking outside the Royal Courts of
OL,16,FJustice in London after the trial had
OL,17,Ffinished, Mr Hibbert thanked his legal
OL,18,Fteam and said he believed it was "an
OL,19,Fextremely important case to bring to
OL,20,Fcourt".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
