OL,3,CArena attack survivor 'shouldn't need
OL,4,Ccourt to prove not faked'
OL,6,FAsked what it was like to come to
OL,7,Fcourt, Mr Hibbert told reporters:
OL,8,F"It's been very difficult ... I had to
OL,9,Ftake a stand, I'm all for freedom of
OL,10,Fspeech but I had to take a stand to
OL,11,Fprotect the most beautiful thing in my
OL,12,Flife, my daughter Eve, and that's what
OL,13,Fthis is about."
OL,15,F"It's been a tough thing to have to
OL,16,Fget through, but I know I've got a lot
OL,17,Fof people supporting me," he added.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
