OL,3,CArena attack survivor 'shouldn't need
OL,4,Ccourt to prove not faked'
OL,6,FSalman Abedi killed 22 people and
OL,7,Finjured hundreds when he detonated the
OL,8,Fhomemade rucksack-bomb in the crowd of
OL,9,Fconcert-goers, with the court told
OL,10,Fthat the Hibberts were some of the
OL,11,Fnearest people to him at the time of
OL,12,Fthe blast.
OL,14,FBut Mr Hall has claimed that several
OL,15,Fof those who died are living abroad or
OL,16,Fwere dead before the attack, telling
OL,17,Fthe court he believed that no-one was
OL,18,F"genuinely injured" in the bombing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
