OL,3,CArena attack survivor 'shouldn't need
OL,4,Ccourt to prove not faked'
OL,6,FIn his closing arguments, Jonathan
OL,7,FPrice, for the Hibberts, said the pair
OL,8,Fwere private individuals.
OL,10,FHe said: "They have suffered the most
OL,11,Fappalling tragedy, not just their
OL,12,Finjuries, physical and psychological,
OL,13,Fbut everything that goes with this."
OL,15,FThe barrister added: "Eve's life was
OL,16,Fjust beginning. She was just
OL,17,Fflourishing at the age of 14. It is
OL,18,Fhard to imagine a greater tragedy,
OL,19,Feven had she died."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
