OL,3,CArena attack survivor 'shouldn't need
OL,4,Ccourt to prove not faked'
OL,6,FMr Price later said Miss Hibbert "is
OL,7,Fan unwilling and unwitting participant
OL,8,Fin the defendant's baseless
OL,9,Fspeculation", calling Mr Hall's
OL,10,Fconduct "objectively harmful" and
OL,11,F"offensive, and known by the defendant
OL,12,Fto be offensive".
OL,14,FPaul Oakley, for Mr Hall, said on
OL,15,FThursday that Mr Hibbert "is not
OL,16,Fsomebody who has shied away from
OL,17,Fpublicity".
OL,19,FHe added that his client, previously
OL,20,Fan engineer, "actually believes what
OL,21,Fhe's saying".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
