OL,3,CArena attack survivor 'shouldn't need
OL,4,Ccourt to prove not faked'
OL,6,FThe barrister said: "It's clear from
OL,7,Fthe evidence, I suggest, and from the
OL,8,Fcross-examination of Mr Hall, it has
OL,9,Fnever been suggested that he is making
OL,10,Fthings up."
OL,12,FMr Oakley later told the court that
OL,13,Fthere had been "no actual contact"
OL,14,Fbetween Mr Hall and Miss Hibbert and
OL,15,Fthat "any distress she has suffered
OL,16,Fhas been imparted to her by her
OL,17,Fparents"
OL,19,FMrs Justice Steyn's written ruling is
OL,20,Fexpected to be released after early
OL,21,FOctober.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
